In 2014 FIFA World Cup qualification – UEFA Group C, Republic of Ireland lose 6–1 to Germany, their joint worst ever competitive defeat and their worst home defeat since 1931. Calls increase for the removal of manager Giovanni Trapattoni. (ESPN) (The Irish Times) (Deutsche Welle) (The Times of India)El Clásico: Real Madrid and Barcelona play a 1–1 draw in the first leg of their 2012–13 Copa del Rey semifinal at Santiago Bernabeu Stadium. Lionel Messi's streak of scoring in 16 straight matches ends. (ESPN) (BBC) (AP via Yahoo!)